snippet.title: Fall Guys - Mobile Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Available through the Epic Games Store on Android worldwide and iOS in the European Union. Read more about it and the Epic Games Store mobile launch here: www.fallguys.com/news/fall-guys-mobile

Run, jump, grab and dive… on the go: FALL GUYS ON MOBILE IS HERE!

Available through the Epic Games Store on Android worldwide and iOS in the European Union. Read more here: www.fallguys.com/news/fall-guys-mobile

Find out all you need on how to download here: www.fallguys.com/download
